</style></div><div class="as-container as-container-stacked as-bg-transparent"><div class="lego-element navbar secondary-nav"id="secondary-nav"><div class="lego-element navbar-container"><nav class="lego-element"><div class="lego-element subnav"><ul class="lego-element nav navbar-nav"><li class="lego-element"><a class="as-link as-link-interaction no-decoration" href="#merchants-benefits" target="_self">特長</a></li><li class="lego-element"><a class="as-link as-link-interaction no-decoration" href="#merchants-benefits__main-container" target="_self">導入のメリット</a></li><li class="lego-element"><a class="as-link as-link-interaction no-decoration" href="#merchants-demo" target="_self">Amazon Pay体験</a></li><li class="lego-element"><a class="as-link as-link-interaction no-decoration" href="#merchants-pricing" target="_self">手数料</a></li><li class="lego-element"><a class="as-link as-link-interaction no-decoration" href="#Reviews_main-container" target="_self">事業者様の声</a></li><li class="lego-element"><a class="as-link as-link-interaction no-decoration" href="#Download_main-container" target="_self">資料ダウンロード</a></li></ul></div></nav></div></div></div><div class="as-container as-container-stacked as-bg-transparent v-pad text-center"><a name="video"></a> <div class="lego-element container text-left--desktop"><div class="lego-element row"><div class="lego-element col-md-6"><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/G/01/EPSMarketingJRubyWebsite/assets/3/images/embedded-video-background.033e654c.png" alt="" title="" class="as-img as-img-theme-icon as-img-theme-image-default img-responsive as-responsive-img" /><div class="lego-element video-bg__video"><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/pfucJZorKvw?enablejsapi=1&version=3&controls=0&rel=0&showinfo=0&modestbranding=1&wmode４=transparent" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" id="YouTubeV1"></iframe></div></div><div class="lego-element col-md-6 margin-top-25--handhelds"><h2 class="as-heading" >Amazon Payは自社ECサイトで簡単・安心な決済を提供するサービスです</h2><div ><p>Amazon Payは最短2クリックでお買い物が完了する決済サービスです。自社ECサイトに導入すれば、新規顧客獲得、コンバージョンアップなど、ビジネスの成長が期待できます。</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="as-container as-container-stacked as-bg-transparent background-wild-sand"id="merchants-benefits"><div class="lego-element container v-pad"><h2 class="as-heading text-center" >Amazon Payの特長</h2><h3 class="as-heading font-default font-size-16 text-center" ><p>Amazon Payは、Amazonアカウントさえあればいつでもどこでもお買い物できる環境を提供します</p>
</h3></div></div><div class="as-container as-container-stacked as-bg-transparent background-wild-sand"><div class="lego-element container v-pad"><div class="lego-element row margin-top-0--desktop child-margin-top-25--handhelds margin-top-30"><div class="lego-element col-sm-4"><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/G/01/EPSMarketingJRubyWebsite/assets/merchantredesign/LockRedesign._V282621305_.png" alt="" title="" class="as-img as-img-theme-icon as-img-theme-image-default as-responsive-img" /><div class="lego-element padding-top-10 padding-bottom-5--flat"><h3 class="as-heading font-default font-size-16" >信頼性が高く、多くの人に選ばれる決済ソリューション</h3></div><div class="font-size-13" ><ul>
	<li>Amazonアカウントさえあれば決済できます</li>
	<li>Amazonで購入するような体験を自社サイトで提供でき、コンバージョン向上をサポート</li>
</ul>
