<p>皆様がお持ちのAmazonアカウントで、Amazon Payが実現するかんたんで安全なお買い物をご体験ください。</p></h3><div class="as-col col-xs-12  col-sm-12  as-hero-height-none as-bg-transparent" ><div class=" as-padding as-padding-xs-no-top as-padding-xs-no-right as-padding-xs-no-bottom as-padding-xs-no-left as-padding-sm-no-top as-padding-sm-no-right as-padding-sm-no-bottom as-padding-sm-no-left text-center"><a class=" as-link no-decoration as-color-blue as-link-interaction amzn-button margin-top-30" rel="noreferrer" href="https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/amazonpay-demoshop-origin/shop-item.html" target="_self">デモサイトを体験する</a><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="as-container as-container-stacked as-bg-transparent text-center v-pad"id="merchants-pricing"><div class="lego-element container"><h2 class="as-heading margin-bottom-10" >Amazon Pay手数料</h2><div ><p>初期費用：無料、月額費用：無料、トランザクション料：不要</p></div><div class="lego-element row margin-top-30 padding-bottom-10"><div class="lego-element col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2"><div class="lego-element row gutter-scale-2 match-height child-margin-top-25--handhelds"><div class="lego-element col-sm-6"><div class="lego-element v-align background-pickled-bluewood"><div class="lego-element color-white padding-v-20"><h4 class="as-heading font-weight-300 color-white margin-top-0 margin-bottom--5" >4%</h4><div ><p>(デジタルコンテンツの販売: 4.5%)</p></div></div></div></div><div class="lego-element col-sm-6 text-left"><table class="lego-element width-full display-table-as-block--handhelds text-center--handhelds"><tbody class="lego-element child-margin-top-10--handhelds"><tr class="lego-element"><td class="lego-element"><div >物理的商品・サービスの販売：</div></td><td class="lego-element"><div >4%</div></td></tr><tr class="lego-element"><td class="lego-element"><div >デジタルコンテンツの販売：</div></td><td class="lego-element"><div >4.5%</div></td></tr><tr class="lego-element"><td class="lego-element"><div ><a href="https://pay.amazon.com/jp/help/201212280">料金についての詳細</a></di